ARM: dts: iwg22d-sodimm: Sound DMA support via DVC on DTS

DMA transfer uses DVC

     DMA               DMApp
[MEM] -> [SRC] -> [DVC] -> [SSIU] -> [SSI]

     DMA               DMApp
[MEM] <- [DVC] <- [SRC] <- [SSIU] <- [SSI]

